author: By JULIE CARR SMYTH and DAN SEWELL Associated Press
title: Democracy in overtime: Candidates await virus-delayed votes
description: CINCINNATI (AP) — Political campaigns in some U.S. states have been switching gears or are in limbo awaiting decisions on voting plans after elections were postponed because of the coronavirus outbreak.
